message.body: Good afternoon how are you?
Good. How are you?
I'm good wishing it wasn't so humid here haha how's your day been?
What city are you in?
I'm in Tucson, AZ until Monday...then Los Angeles.
Day`s okay. Just had my first laser Tattoo removal session. Ouch!
I'm in NYC I was actually just in Arizona on vacation at the Grand Canyon, it's so nice out there!
Ah I've heard that's painful! How many sessions will you have to have? Why are you getting it removed?
I LOVE NYC! I've lived in 4 of the 5 Burroughs. Which one do you live in?
Probably 4-6 sessions. the guy who did it 15 yrs ago messed it up. Bothered me all this time. Then I started a cover up 3 yrs ago, and the girl messed th
at up! So I figured I gotta get it light enough to get it covered up once and for all!
I live in queens! I love NYC but I've been here for 5 years now and I'm starting to want to move somewhere else! It's a great place though I love th city!
That's crazy that your tattoo got messed up twice! Hope you can get it fixed up right this time!
Isn't there a show about people getting tattoo cover ups? You should go on it! Haha
I lived in Sunnyside, QNS - right off the 7!
Where are you thinking of going? I lived in many, many cities...
Awesome! I live by St. John's now but am moving to Astoria in August.
I think I want to I somewhere that doesn't get cold hahah I hate winter!
I loved Astoria! Great food! cool shops.
Yeah I'm excited to live closer to the city and also to have all those cool bars and restaurants right nearby
